ank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/external_publications/EP71351.html</guid></item><item><title>ULA（United to House LA）转让税措施对洛杉矶经济发展和市政财政的影响</title><link>https://www.rand.org/pubs/research_reports/RRA4928-1.html</link><description>&lt;img height="90" src="https://www.rand.org/content/rand/pubs/research_reports/RRA4928-1/_jcr_content/par/teaser.crop.160x90.cm.jpeg/1779976512726.jpeg" width="160" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p class="desc"&gt; ULA 措施已为经济适用房筹集了 12 亿美元，但导致高价值房地产销售减少了 31%，并阻止了 9,000 多套新住房的建设，到 2026 年初，洛杉矶的收入损失超过 4.52 亿美元。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;"&gt;（使用&lt;a href="https://fetchrss.com/feedLink?w=67d7ba1d141b09f2900edc32" target="_blank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/research_reports/RRA4928-1.html</guid></item><item><title>患有糖尿病下肢伤口的医疗保险患者截肢的地理差异</title><link>https://www.rand.org/pubs/external_publications/EP71286.html</link><description>&lt;p class="desc"&gt;本文的目的是研究区域患者和医疗保健系统特征与糖尿病下肢伤口后大截肢的关系。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;"&gt;（使用&lt;a href="https://fetchrss.com/feedLink?w=67d7ba1d141b09f2900edc32" target="_blank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/external_publications/EP71286.html</guid></item></channel></rss>